Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:30.47,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}あの日のリズム今に刻む
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.21,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(120,0)}Yes reaching out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:36.77,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}Walk 遠くに見てた未来掴んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:39.88,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5}Red pulse rushing through and I can hear you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:42.97,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}溢れたノイズをかき鳴らす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:48.43,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(0,200)}未来図は泡のように
